                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120701-74-off435 t18120701-74-cd436"></join>, a watch, value 30 s, the property of 
                     <persName id="t18120701-74-victim670" type="victimName">
                        Andries 
                        Matthias
                     <interp inst="t18120701-74-victim670" type="surname" value="Matthias"></interp>
