               <p>- BROWN. I am an officer. I produce the two handkerchiefs I received from Mrs. Murray.</p>
               <p>Mrs. Murray. These are the two handkerchiefs Antony brought into my room. I washed them for Antony.</p>
               <p>ISLOS DE LOS SANTOS. They are my handkerchiefs. They were taken from my chest.</p>
